The only issue is when they run out!  When I asked a good friend what did she want from Chicago, right away she said "Garrett Popcorn!" - I had no idea about them until she told me.  Fortunately you will see lots of these shops around Chicago.  When I was there they had a great promotion, buy one classic tin get one free in honor of breast cancer awareness.  I got their famous cheese mixed with Almond Caramel.  They are known for their combinations, and make your own combos.  When I was in line the guy in front of me was from Boston and raved about this popcorn.  He told me which combo to get and he was right.  Now you know - a great gift to bring home from Chicago-Garrett's Popcorn!  If you forget to buy it in town, they are shops at the airport, but only certain terminals and concourses, so PLAN AHEAD!
